text: 235px ' (November 17, 1630 – June 29, 1666) was a Japanese daimyō of the Edo period, who ruled the Tokushima Domain. His court title was Awa no kami. ==Family== * Father: Hachisuka Tadateru * Mother: Reishoin (d.1655) * Wife: Kinhime (d.1703) * Concubine: Inai no Kata * Children: ** Hachisuka Tsunamichi by Kinhime ** Yukihime married Niwa Nagatsugu by Inai no Kata ==Reference== Category:1630 births Category:1666 deaths Category:Daimyo Category:Hachisuka clan
title: Hachisuka Mitsutaka
